William B. TRESCOTT, petitioner,
v.
FEDERAL MOTOR CARRIER SAFETY ADMINISTRATION, et al. No. 13-509. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 13, 2014.

Case below, American Trucking Associations, Inc. v. Federal Motor Carrier Safety Admin., 724 F.3d 243 .

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit denied.
